*Zahvaljujući* njihovoj uspešnoj saradnji, uspeli su da ostvare svoje ciljeve. (Thanks to their successful collaboration, they managed to achieve their goals.)

Njegov uspeh *zahvaljujući* svojoj radnoj etici bio je bez premca. (His success, thanks to his work ethic, was unparalleled.)

*Zahvaljujući* modernim tehnologijama, nove mogućnosti su se otvorile. (Thanks to modern technologies, new possibilities have opened up.)

Njegov uspeh *zahvaljujući* njegovom predanom radu bio je bez premca. (Thanks to his dedicated work, his success was unparalleled.) 

*Zahvaljujući* njihovoj pomoći, uspeli smo da obezbedimo sve što je potrebno. (Thanks to their help, we managed to secure everything that was needed.)